# Best Practices

## Purpose
To ensure all development follows high standards for code quality, maintainability, and collaboration across the agentic ecosystem.

- Follow established coding standards and guidelines.
- Maintain clean, readable, and well-documented code.
- Implement comprehensive testing for all agents.
- Prioritize security and performance in all designs.
- Ensure clear communication and standardized interfaces.
- Schedule regular maintenance and updates.
- Avoid unnecessary addition or removal of lines in files. Prefer minimal, focused changes that only modify what is required.
